             was indicted for <rs id="t18191201-28-off170" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18191201-28-off170" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18191201-28-off170" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18191201-28-cd171" type="crimeDate">9th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18191201-28-off170 t18191201-28-cd171"></join>, one watch, value 3 l.; one piece of ribbon value 1 d., and one key, value 5 s., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18191201-28-victim384" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Sharp
                        <interp inst="t18191201-28-victim384" type="surname" value="Sharp"></interp>
